==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: bloodsucking
<hw>bloodsucking</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>drawing blood
from the body of another; <as>as, a plague of <ex>bloodsucking</ex>
insects</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>having the nature or habits of a parasite or leech;
living off another; -- of plants or persons; <as>as, a
<ex>bloodsucking</ex> blackmailer; <ex>bloodsucking</ex>
lawyers</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> parasitic, parasitical, leechlike.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bloodthirsty</ent>⟦br⟧
